Next, the current structure uses sequential blocks without any residual connections. Introducing skip connections might allow the network to learn deeper representations more effectively.

Additionally, the model currently doesn't use attention mechanisms, which have proven effective in many vision tasks. Incorporating self-attention could enhance feature extraction.

